    "description": "unerry,Inc. operates real behavior data platforms in Japan. It offers Shopper Miel, a shopper analytics tool; Shopping congestion map, a tool that provides congestion tendency by day of the week and time zone near stores, such as supermarkets and drug stores; and Customized congestion map, a tool that automatically estimates store/event congestion. The company also provides Beacon Bank AD, a tool that optimizes advertising by identifying targets, timings, and locations that are likely to be visited and deliver real-time push and social media ads; Beacon Bank 1to1, a build integrated marketing platform; and Real behavior data visualization/analysis, a tool that provides AI analysis of accumulated monthly big data of approximately 84 billion people, and visualization and analysis. In addition, it offers advertising services. unerry,Inc. was incorporated in 2015 and is based in Tokyo, Japan."
